<h1>YOUR BEST FRIEND</h1>

<p>Dogs. There's a reason we call them man's best friend. We can learn so many things from a dog's behavior, personality, demeanor, resiliency, and most importantly, the willingness to provide their family members with unconditional love, loyalty, and companionship down to their very last breath.</p>

<h2>Reasons Why Dogs Are Man’s Best Friend</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Dogs never judge you.</li>
  <li>They’re hands down the best listeners</li>
  <li>They’re always excited to see you, regardless of how long you spent apart.</li>
  <li>You can undoubtedly count on their loyalty</li>
  <li>A dog will never criticize you</li>
  <li>And they're seldom in a bad mood</li>
  <li>They know how to appreciate the simple things</li>
</ol>

<h3>Hiperlink</h3>

<a href="https://www.theodysseyonline.com/reasons-dogs-mans-best-friend">Understand the reasons</a>

